             sworn.</p>
               <p>I am a Patten maker, I have known him about twelve years, his father is a Castor and casts buckles, I take the <rs id="t17840421-64-deflabel356" type="occupation">boy</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t17840421-64-defend767 t17840421-64-deflabel356"></join> to be about fifteen, I never knew any harm of him before.</p>
